  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study was prospective randomized double-blinded clinical trial on patients with thyroid
      disease who underwent thyroidectomy in the general surgery department, Mansoura university
      hospitals during the period of February 2017 to February 2018.Two techniques for vascular
      sealing were compared: conventional tying and harmonic scalpel
    </textblock>
